data.description: Immaculately maintained custom built rancher w/wrap-around covered porch boasts 3073 sqft with an attached 3 car garage situated on 6.15 level treed acres plus a 40x60 heated shop with lean-to! This impressive home features a massive great room with gorgeous hand-scraped birch hardwood floors, vaulted ceilings with knotty pine cedar and a real rock fireplace with oversized Swedish firebox. Enjoy the open concept floor plan with split bedroom design featuring rustic alder crown molding in all 3 bedrooms, solid rustic alder interior doors, full trim windows, handcrafted custom light fixtures throughout, exterior doors from all 3 bedrooms and plenty of storage. The oversized master suite offers a cozy fireplace, French doors leading to covered deck, large master bath with a walk-in tiled shower and dual shower heads plus a huge walk-in closet. This grand home is only minutes to Farragut State Park, Bayview, Lake Pend Oreille, boat ramp, and more!
